 1 large lemon or any flavour cake mix 1 3-3/4 pkg Jello Lemon Instant pudding 1 cup water ½ cup oil 4 eggs Mix all together.
TOPPING;
Ingredients 2 tbsp cinnamon ½ cup brown sugar ½ cup chopped walnuts Instructions Grease tube pan. Sprinkle half topping mixture. Pour half of cake mixture. Add rest …

WHITE SAUCE;
1 cup milk 4 tbsp flour Cook as for white sauce, and let cool.
BEAT WELL;
Ingredients 1 cup butter or margarine 1 cup white sugar 1 tsp vanilla. Instructions When sauce is cooled, add the butter and sugar mixture, and BEAT WELL.
Makes enough for a layer cake.
